    "description": "“无限板块”是一款拼图类的解密游戏。<br><br>游戏中的目标是用蓝色的拼块填满每一关中里面的灰色区域，拼块放置的顺序是解密的关键。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050190/extras/51c947fe3f590b54d041d27830e32c27.poster.avif?t=1718429449\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050190/extras/51c947fe3f590b54d041d27830e32c27.webm?t=1718429449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050190/extras/51c947fe3f590b54d041d27830e32c27.mp4?t=1718429449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏里的拼块拥有各种不同的特殊效果，例如在放下的时候会旋转或者移动别的拼块。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050190/extras/6e1e4c4ebace10f6675b274a998fb250.webp?t=1718429449\" width=32 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050190/extras/790d43ec61a5884c267c0e7bf037fdc2.webp?t=1718429449\" width=32 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050190/extras/9d0661ffa90a415418fb82e6f2e6ff93.webp?t=1718429449\" width=32 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050190/extras/b75d3fc9d2138cb3566efef60e9048a4.webp?t=1718429449\" width=32 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050190/extras/bfbc420ba82ab205846264791e46fa3a.webp?t=1718429449\" width=32 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050190/extras/7cc860655869f